data.description: Endless possibilities with 7 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this property is perfect for a large family, those seeking multi-generational living, or investors looking for rental income potential. The versatile layout provides ample space to craft your ideal living arrangements. Transform one of the bedrooms into a home office, create a dedicated gym, or establish an artist's studio the options are limitless.  The expansive fenced-in yard is one of the highlights of this property. Whether you envision it as a playground for children or a safe haven for pets this outdoor space offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and relaxation.  While this home boasts historic charm, it's in need of some TLC to fully realize its potential. Bring your vision and expertise to restore this grand home
